description: Fungie, the world's oldest solitary dolphin, has not been seen in his 37-year harbour home for a week.
title: Fungie: The missing dolphin who became an Irish star
title_page: Fungie: The missing dolphin who became an Irish star - BBC News
maintext: "That is my swimming pool and having another living breathing animal in there who just trots alone with you in the winter is a lovely feeling - just that someone else is breathing with you in the water," she said.
